hopobject.body: Directory enquiries valproic acid rxlist Suddenly, Scotland's centuries-old love of sugar takes on a sinister complexion. What seemed a peccadillo, a national predilection far less serious than our love of the deep fat frier or the so-called amber nectar, is shown as unhealthy, irresponsible, and potentially toxic. A surfeit of sugar is now being held directly responsible for the rise in diabetes in younger people, and for many cases of high blood pressure, heart and pulmonary disease. Soon it may even overtake tobacco for its ill effect on the heart.
